## Standards

- OGC API - EDR Part 1: Core
- OGC API - EDR Part 2: PubSub
- OGC API - EDR Part 3: Service Profiles (draft)
- OGC API - Processes Part 1
- OpenAPI 3.0 / AsyncAPI 3.0
- Metanorma/AsciiDoc documentation format

